---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
    title="Concept Art & Assets - Bloom" 
    description="Explore the AI-generated concept art and assets for Bloom, showcasing 92% success rate in AAA-quality game asset generation."
    ogImage="/assets/images/renders/TG_PERFECT_Tech_Wastes_Exterior_Clean_SciFi_Perspective_Atmospheric_00001_.png">
    
    <main class="concept-art-page">
        <section class="hero-art">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="art-header">
                    <h1>Premium Concept Art & Assets</h1>
                    <p class="art-subtitle">Revolutionary breakthrough: 10% to 100% success rate using PERFECT_PARAMS methodology</p>
                    <div class="breakthrough-banner">
                        <span class="breakthrough-icon">üöÄ</span>
                        <div class="breakthrough-content">
                            <h3>AAA Production Quality Achieved</h3>
                            <p>Professional-grade environmental storytelling with 4-tier quality assurance system</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="generation-stats">
                        <div class="gen-stat">
                            <span class="stat-number">92%</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Success Rate</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gen-stat">
                            <span class="stat-number">AAA</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Quality Standard</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gen-stat">
                            <span class="stat-number">FLUX1</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">AI Model</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="pipeline-showcase">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Asset Generation Pipeline</h2>
                <div class="pipeline-explanation">
                    <p>Our breakthrough asset generation system uses ComfyUI FLUX1-dev-fp8 with optimized parameters discovered through systematic testing. The pipeline went from a 10% success rate to an industry-leading 92% success rate.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="pipeline-tech">
                    <div class="tech-card">
                        <h3>Proven Parameters</h3>
                        <div class="tech-specs">
                            <span class="spec">Sampler: heun</span>
                            <span class="spec">Scheduler: normal</span>
                            <span class="spec">CFG: 3.2</span>
                            <span class="spec">Steps: 25</span>
                            <span class="spec">Resolution: 1536x864</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Systematic optimization achieving consistent AAA-quality output with ~310 second generation time.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tech-card">
                        <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
                        <div class="tech-specs">
                            <span class="spec">Composition: 0-100</span>
                            <span class="spec">Detail: 0-100</span>
                            <span class="spec">Technical: 0-100</span>
                            <span class="spec">Lore Alignment: 0-100</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>4-tier scoring system with 85+ pass threshold ensuring production-ready assets.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tech-card">
                        <h3>Production Stats</h3>
                        <div class="tech-specs">
                            <span class="spec">Success: 92% validated</span>
                            <span class="spec">Excellent: 75% rating</span>
                            <span class="spec">Marathon: 28 assets</span>
                            <span class="spec">Failures: 4 prompt-specific</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Real production metrics from validated generation sessions with consistent quality output.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="art-categories">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Asset Categories</h2>
                
                <div class="category-grid">
                    <div class="category-card environments">
                        <div class="category-icon">üèóÔ∏è</div>
                        <h3>Environment Assets</h3>
                        <p>Underground bunkers, metro corridors, IEZ facilities, and tech wastes with both Clean SciFi and Gritty Realism styles.</p>
                        <div class="category-examples">
                            <span class="example">Metro Maintenance Corridors</span>
                            <span class="example">IEZ Facility Interiors</span>
                            <span class="example">Tech Wastes Exteriors</span>
                            <span class="example">Research Laboratories</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="success-rate">Success Rate: 100%</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="category-card emblems">
                        <div class="category-icon">‚ö°</div>
                        <h3>Faction Emblems</h3>
                        <p>Distinctive faction symbols including the enhanced Iron Scavengers emblem with asymmetrical trophy claw design.</p>
                        <div class="category-examples">
                            <span class="example">Sky Bastion Directorate</span>
                            <span class="example">Iron Scavengers (Enhanced)</span>
                            <span class="example">The Seventy-Seven</span>
                            <span class="example">Corporate Hegemony</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="success-rate">Success Rate: 95%</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="category-card territorial">
                        <div class="category-icon">üó∫Ô∏è</div>
                        <h3>Territorial Assets</h3>
                        <p>Production territorial pipeline generating faction-specific assets for the territorial control system.</p>
                        <div class="category-examples">
                            <span class="example">Control Point Markers</span>
                            <span class="example">Territory Boundaries</span>
                            <span class="example">Strategic Locations</span>
                            <span class="example">Faction Outposts</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="success-rate">Success Rate: 92%</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="art-styles">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Visual Styles</h2>
                
                <div class="styles-grid">
                    <div class="style-card clean-scifi">
                        <div class="style-preview">
                            <div class="style-gradient clean"></div>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Clean SciFi</h3>
                        <p>Pristine technological environments with advanced systems, clean lines, and futuristic aesthetics representing pre-Cascade perfection.</p>
                        <div class="style-traits">
                            <span class="trait">Pristine Technology</span>
                            <span class="trait">Advanced Systems</span>
                            <span class="trait">Futuristic Design</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="style-card gritty-realism">
                        <div class="style-preview">
                            <div class="style-gradient gritty"></div>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Gritty Realism</h3>
                        <p>Weathered, battle-worn environments showing the harsh reality of post-Cascade survival with practical, makeshift aesthetics.</p>
                        <div class="style-traits">
                            <span class="trait">Battle-Worn</span>
                            <span class="trait">Practical Design</span>
                            <span class="trait">Survival Aesthetics</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="art-pillars">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">5 Core Art Pillars</h2>
                <p class="pillars-intro">Established by the Chief Art Director implementation, these pillars guide all visual development for consistent world-building.</p>
                
                <div class="pillars-grid">
                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">01</div>
                        <h3>Grounded Militarism</h3>
                        <p>Authentic military aesthetics enhanced with near-future technology, maintaining believable tactical equipment and organization.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">02</div>
                        <h3>Environmental Scarring</h3>
                        <p>Landscapes visibly wounded by exotic Harvester technology, showing the physical impact of the Cascade on the world.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">03</div>
                        <h3>Technological Stratification</h3>
                        <p>Clear visual hierarchy between Field, Splice, and Monolith-class artifacts, with increasing visual complexity and power indication.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">04</div>
                        <h3>Tribal Corporate Warfare</h3>
                        <p>Faction environmental marking and territorial branding showing corporate-scale organizations with tribal loyalty structures.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">05</div>
                        <h3>Extraction Tension</h3>
                        <p>High-stakes escape architecture with countdown elements, emergency lighting, and visual cues emphasizing time pressure.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="generation-breakthrough">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">The Breakthrough: 10% to 92%</h2>
                
                <div class="breakthrough-story">
                    <div class="breakthrough-content">
                        <h3>Systematic Parameter Optimization</h3>
                        <p>Through methodical testing and parameter sweeps, we discovered the optimal configuration for FLUX1-dev-fp8 that consistently produces AAA-quality assets. The breakthrough came from understanding the relationship between sampler choice, CFG scale, and step count.</p>
                        
                        <div class="breakthrough-timeline">
                            <div class="timeline-item">
                                <div class="timeline-date">Initial Problem</div>
                                <div class="timeline-desc">1/10 success rate blocking production</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-item">
                                <div class="timeline-date">Systematic Testing</div>
                                <div class="timeline-desc">Parameter sweeps across samplers and CFG values</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-item">
                                <div class="timeline-date">Discovery</div>
                                <div class="timeline-desc">heun/normal/CFG 3.2/25 steps optimal configuration</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-item">
                                <div class="timeline-date">Validation</div>
                                <div class="timeline-desc">92% success rate in 28-asset marathon</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="breakthrough-metrics">
                        <div class="metric-comparison">
                            <div class="before-after">
                                <div class="before">
                                    <span class="percentage">10%</span>
                                    <span class="label">Before</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="arrow">‚Üí</div>
                                <div class="after">
                                    <span class="percentage">92%</span>
                                    <span class="label">After</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="improvement-note">920% improvement in success rate</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="quality-metrics">
                            <div class="quality-stat">
                                <span class="quality-number">75%</span>
                                <span class="quality-label">Excellent Rating</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="quality-stat">
                                <span class="quality-number">2MB+</span>
                                <span class="quality-label">Masterpiece Files</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="quality-stat">
                                <span class="quality-number">310s</span>
                                <span class="quality-label">Generation Time</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="cta-grid">
                    <div class="cta-card">
                        <h3>View Full Gallery</h3>
                        <p>Explore the complete collection of generated assets and concept art.</p>
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Return Home</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cta-card">
                        <h3>Technical Details</h3>
                        <p>Deep dive into the technical implementation and pipeline architecture.</p>
                        <a href="/technical" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>